long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SQL Parser is a handy Chrome extension that allows you to automatically extract all table names used in an SQL query. Simply input your SQL language code, and the extension will quickly analyze and parse the code, identifying all the table names mentioned in the query. This can greatly speed up your workflow when working with SQL databases, as you no longer need to manually search for and extract table names from complex queries. With SQL Parser, you can efficiently analyze and understand your SQL code, making database development and debugging easier and more efficient.
